What fun to watch this darling telenovela!  This charming story, staring a great cast, focuses on the main character, a little girl, who is Carita de Angel herself.  Children and adults will find the adventures of Carita de Angel, or Maria, as she is known to her family, a refreshingly light hearted view on a slice of life in the Latin world.  If you are trying to learn Spanish, like I am and want to hear real world conversation, this is a fun road to travel down.
